Rollerslam version 1.0

Components:
 - Environment/SimulationServer (environment.jar)
 - LogServer (infrastructure.jar, logging.jar, hsqldb.jar)
 - Repeater (repeater.jar)
 - MobileRepeater (mobile-display.jar)
 - Display (display.jar)
 - MobileDisplay (RollerslamMobile.jad, RollerslamMobile.jar, microemulator.jar)
 - Agents (testagent.jar)
 - LogDisplay (logplayer.jar)

How-to execute:
 - LogServer - OPTIONAL
   * java -Xms512m -Xmx1024m -cp infrastructure.jar rollerslam.infrastructure.logging.LogRecordingServiceImpl
   - LogServer will salve the log at folder "c:\temp"

 - Environment/SimulationServer
   * java -jar environment.jar <logServerIP>
   - <logServerIP> = IP LogServer. If logServerIP is not declared, the environment will starts the LogServer in itself.

 - Agents
   * java -cp testagent.jar rollerslam.agent.goalbased.RollerslamGoalBasedAgent <team> <environmentIP>
   - <team> = Team of agent. Can be only "A" or "B"
   - <environemtIP> = IP of Environment/SimulationServer or can be "auto" that will automatic find the simulation and connect.

 - Repeater
   * java -jar repeater.jar

 - Display
   * java -jar display.jar

 - MobileRepeater
   * java -jar mobile-display.jar

 - MobileDisplay
   * java -jar microemulator.jar RollerslamMobile.jad

 - LogDisplay
   * java -jar logplayer.jar



